    <guid isPermaLink="false"><![CDATA[https://diensabyansah.com/how-we-build-signature-product-notes/]]></guid>
    <description></description>
    <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Strong product notes explain value in one glance. We focus on construction, material, and intended wear context—then keep language precise.</p><p>Each note starts with what makes the piece distinct, followed by one practical benefit. This gives customers confidence and reduces uncertainty before purchase.</p><p>Great product copy is concise, truthful, and visual. It should feel like guidance from a stylist, not marketing noise.</p>]]></content:encoded>
    <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[A simple framework for writing product notes that sell quality, not hype.]]></excerpt:encoded>
