    <guid isPermaLink="false"><![CDATA[https://diensabyansah.com/whats-next-for-diensa-by-ansah/]]></guid>
    <description></description>
    <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The next phase of Diensa by Ansah is focused on intentional growth. We are expanding collections, improving lead times, and deepening product consistency across categories.</p><p>At the same time, we are investing in editorial storytelling to document process, people, and craft. This helps customers connect with the value behind every garment.</p><p>As partnerships expand, our core remains unchanged: build modern African luxury with discipline, dignity, and long-term impact.</p>]]></content:encoded>
    <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Our next chapter centers on scale, storytelling, and global partnerships rooted in African excellence.]]></excerpt:encoded>
